<br>
Here's the answer:  kill something like a rat.  Now, target the corpse.  Now, cast your level 1 evocation spell over and over on the corpse till you're out of mana.  Sit down, med, repeat.<br>
<br>
Not that I suggest this as a viable method, as you'll spend several hours just working up your spells.  Nor do I ever want to group with someone who PL'ed up to 40, as they'll be fairly clueless.  But this is exactly the method I used as a wizard after each level, just to make sure my spell schools were maxed.<br>
<br>
